snippet.title: EVAVERSE Wonderland Holiday Event
snippet.description:
Evaverse Wonderland is a 10 day holiday event for players to enjoy a festive version of the game with 2x Hoverboard XP, Festive NFTs to win through Tickets, and a wonderful snow-themed map to race on!

Join the Event:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1628750/Evaverse/

Join the Discord Community:
HTTP://www.discord.gg/evaverse

#playtoearn #nftgames
